{
  "1": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\"My heart pounds when I think about that.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "2": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Listen, all of you, to the thunder,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "which is like God's voice.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "3": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "He sends thunder all across the sky,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and he sends lighting to the most distant places on the earth.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "4": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "After the lightning flashes, we hear the thunder,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "which is like God's powerful voice;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "when he speaks, he does not keep back the lightning.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "5": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "When God speaks, it causes us to fear him and admire him, as thunder does;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "he does amazing things that we cannot understand.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "6": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "He commands the snow to fall on the ground,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and often he makes it rain very hard.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "7": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "When God does that, it prevents people from working,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "in order that all people may know that he is the one who does these things.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "8": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "When it rains, the animals go into their hiding places,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and they stay there until the rain stops.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "9": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The storms come from the place in the south where they start,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and the cold winds come from the north.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "10": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "In the winter water freezes when he commands it,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and the lakes become ice.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "11": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "God fills the clouds with moisture,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and lightning flashes everywhere from the clouds.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "12": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "He guides the clouds and causes them to move back and forth\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "in order that they may accomplish all that he commands them to do all over the world.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "13": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Sometimes God sends rain to punish us, sometimes to water the land that he has made,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and sometimes because he wants to be very kind to us.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "14": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Job, listen to this;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "stop and think about the wonderful things that God does.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "15": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Do you know how God commands the lightning to flash down from his clouds?\n\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "16": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Do you know how God decides where to place the clouds in the sky?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Can you understand all the wonderful things that God does,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and how he knows everything and he knows them completely?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "17": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "No, you just sweat there in your hot clothing\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "because even the clothes you wear become very hot.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Your clothing becomes hot because the heat builds up \n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "when the wind comes from the south.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "18": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Can you stretch out the skies like God does and make them as hard as a metal mirror?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "19": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Job, you know so much! So tell us what we should say to God;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "we do not know anything about how we should defend ourselves.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "20": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Should I ask someone to tell God that I want to speak to him?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "No, because if I did that, he might destroy me.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "21": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "You know that people cannot look directly at the sun\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "when it shines brightly in the sky after the wind has blown the clouds away;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "likewise we certainly cannot look at the brightness of God.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "22": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "God comes out of the north with a light that shines like gold;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "his glory causes us to be afraid.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "23": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Almighty God has very great power,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and we do not know how to go near to him.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "He always acts righteously,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and he will never mistreat us.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "24": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "That is the reason that we have an awesome respect for him;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "he does not pay attention to those who proudly, but wrongly, think that they are wise.\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      }
    ]
  },
  "front": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  }
}